Ranger Help for: treat armor
=============================

SYNTAX:      treat <armor>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to treat a piece of leather armor using
natural agents, improving its protective qualities. The armor must be
leather or studded leather for the treatment to work. The effectiveness
of the treatment depends on the Ranger's skill level and knowledge of
the terrain. Treating armor is one of the ways Rangers maintain their
gear without relying on civilization.
